com.google.enterprise.connector.spi

Interface AuthenticationIdentity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleAuthenticationIdentity

    public interface AuthenticationIdentity
    Interface for the identity parameter of the AuthenticationManager.authenticate method. If an implementation overrides the {# toString} method, it should not include the password in the returned string.
